main event: On June 23, 1966, a red colored object was observed in the sky over Hamburg, New York for about 3-4 minutes.
interesting points: The object hovered in the sky and appeared to back up,The witnesses compared the object to an automobile tail light,There was a notation that no physical evidence was found,The report stated that the description was consistent with that of an aircraft, The sighting was documented in a Project Blue Book Record form.
